<h1>New Flickr User Claim Request</h1>

<p>
  A user has requested to claim a Flickr user account.
</p>

<h2>Details</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Photonia User:</strong> <%= h @user.email %> (#<%= h @user.serial_number %>)</li>
  <li><strong>Flickr Username:</strong> <%= h @flickr_user.username %></li>
  <li><strong>Flickr NSID:</strong> <%= h @flickr_user.nsid %></li>
  <li><strong>Flickr Profile:</strong> <a href="<%= h @flickr_user.profileurl %>"><%= h @flickr_user.profileurl %></a></li>
  <li><strong>Claim Type:</strong> Manual</li>
  <% if @reason.present? %>
  <li><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= h @reason %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<h2>Actions</h2>

<p>
  Please review and manage this claim in the user administration interface:
</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @user_admin_url %>">View User and Manage Claim</a>
</p>

<p>
  Your friendly Photonia bot.
</p>
